
  <div class="module module-white module-user-card">
    <h1>恭喜您，商品购买成功！</h1>
    <div class="module-table-box">
      <table class="table table-bordered">
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>订单金额</td>
            <td>￥<%= @order[:totalamount] %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>订单编号</td>
            <td><%= @order[:orderno] %></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <div class="module-wrapper module-btn text-center">
      <button class="btn btn-large btn-danger btn-block" id="follow_button" value="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3NTQyMzcyNw==&mid=200211171&idx=1&sn=212ce2198c574df483359d817ec7a4a4&scene=1&from=singlemessage&isappinstalled=0&key=bdc0fc08be7dd6d4253502098c36d92c47b6b8d0de93638f587afcd53b17d39290dc3b1a9225eff6857d3e7a6d801fdd&ascene=0&uin=Mjk5NzcyNjE1">关注银泰百货北京分公司</button>
    </div>
    <div class="module-btn text-center">
      <button class="btn btn-large btn-danger btn-block" id="show_button" value="<%= ims_order_path(@order[:orderno]) %>">查看订单详情</button>
    </div>
    <div class="module module-notice">
      <h4><i class="fa fa-exclamation-circle"></i> 温馨提示</h4>
      <ol>
        <li>如果您还未关注我们的公众号，后期将无法查看订单信息，请务必点击以下链接关注我们。</li>
        <li>非常感谢您订购银泰百货商品，我们将尽快为您发货，祝您购物愉快！</li>
        <li>为了确保您所购买的商品库存充足，我们的工作人员将会尽快和您确认订单信息，由此给您带来不便，敬请谅解。</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </div>



  <% content_for :javascripts do %>
    <script>
      $(function(){

        $(document).on("click", "#follow_button, #show_button", function(){
          url = $(this).attr("value")
          $("#loading-box").modal()
          setTimeout(function(){
            window.location.href = url
          }, 1)
        })
      })
    </script>
  <% end %>
